title: Bug 121170 - get column label from meta data object should return user recognizable strings
OB: The method 'get column label' returns null for the labels before extraction, but after extraction, it returns recognizable strings.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Call the 'get column label' method on a meta data object.
2. Extract the labels from the meta data object.
3. Compare the labels before and after extraction.
